ygData.msgSnippet: Greetings Ladies, I play a High Elf/Cleric on the Tarrew Marr server.  I am level 12 and can hardly wait until I reach level 14 to obtain better spells.
ygData.messageBody:
Greetings Ladies,

I play a High Elf/Cleric on the Tarrew Marr server. I am level 12 and can
hardly wait until I reach level 14 to obtain better spells.

Flirting? I think it is all in fun within the context of the game, and I do
enjoying flirting in return. I've only had one guy cross the line. Since I was
not about to leave the game because of him, I just told him my father was Mr.
Verant and he better get lost fast! Hehehe - needless to say, haven't heard
from him since.

Tara Lea wrote:

> From: Tara Lea <dactyl5@...>
>
> Hi,
>
> I play a High Elf Enchantress on the Innoruuk server name Aegea. I just
> made lvl 9 (I know, not high by all means) and am hoping to get to 12 soon
> for the next spells. I hope to hear from you all and look forward to the
> topics on this list...
>
> -A
